<body>
  <span><!--empty cause we are not adding extra buttons--></span>
  <div class="scrollable">
    <h2>Brief Introduction</h2>
    You can view songs and songbooks by selecting one from the appropriate button.<br/><br/>
    <b>To create a new song or songbook:</b>
    <ul>
      <b>To create a song:</b><br/>
      - Select Create Song.<br/>
      - You can upload a song exported from SongSelect as a .usr file<br/>
      - Or import a song from PraiseTown.com<br/>
      - To add chords, place the chord in a line above the letter to which it's position belongs.<br/>
      <!--    - Format<a href="http://god-is.mine.nu/~song/trac/wiki?p=SongFormat">[link]</a>-->
    </ul>
    <ul>
      <b>To create a songbook:</b><br/>
      - Select Create Songbook<br/>
      - Songs are added from the list on the right, and can be arranged by drag and drop. List is searchable<br/>
      <!--    - Format<a href="http://god-is.mine.nu/~song/trac/wiki?p=SongBookFormat">[link]</a> -->
    </ul>
    
    <h5>Icons from <a href="http://www.famfamfam.com/lab/icons/silk/">http://www.famfamfam.com/lab/icons/silk/</a></h5>
  </div>
